    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this beauty in person! It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car since day one and it is in absolutely perfect, flawless condition. Not a single scratch or door ding to be found, and the interior still has that fresh new car smell! It drives like an absolute dream and has been kept tucked away in a climate-controlled garage. I\u2019m only selling because I need the space, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Let's get you behind the wheel!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
