    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Offering a museum-grade 2004 BMW M3 (E46) in Carbon Black. This specimen features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering linear power through individual throttle bodies to an 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission is crisp, paired with a perfectly calibrated limited-slip differential for superior corner-exit traction. This vehicle has undergone a comprehensive preventative maintenance suite, including a Vanos system overhaul, subframe reinforcement, and a precise valve shim adjustment. The suspension geometry remains factory-tight, and the exterior finish shows zero clear coat failure or oxidation. A mechanically flawless, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
